assistance grants of 1 million dollars for capacity building in
Thailand's water sector and 750,000 dollars to restructure the
Thai Ministry of Agriculture and Cooperatives for improved
governance.
</P>
<P>
The ADB loan is from the bank's ordinary capital resources and
will be repayable in 15 years, including a grace period of three
years, it added. 
