<HEADLINE> Xinhua World News Summary At 1530 GMT, September 23 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON -- Former Chilean leader Augusto Pinochet will have a
medical check on Thursday, local press reported.
</P>
<P>
