heavyweight NAB recovering to 14.9 U.S. dollars. Commonwealth Bank
gained 36 cents to 15.27 U.S. dollars, Westpac bank added 10 cents
to 6.23 U.S. dollars and ANZ bank firmed four cents to 6.73 U.S.
dollars.
</P>
