<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, September 23 (Xinhua) -- The Inter-Parliamentary Union
(IPU) will hold its 102nd statutory conference and related
meetings in Berlin on October 10-16, the Geneva-based organization
announced here Thursday.
</P>
<P>
German President Johannes Rau will open the conference to be
attended by representatives of the 138 parliaments affiliated to
the IPU and those of the five associated regional parliamentary
assemblies.
</P>
