deliberations to generate useful inputs towards the establishment
of the Trans-ASEAN Energy Network which covers the Trans-ASEAN
Power Grid and the Trans- ASEAN Gas Pipeline, ASEAN Council on
Petroleum, the forum organizer, said in a statement Thursday.
