<TEXT>
<P>
CARACAS, September 22 (Xinhua) -- Colombia's rebel group will
meet with the country's peace mediator Thursday in Venezuela,
Venezuelan Vice Foreign Minister Jorge Valero said here Wednesday.
</P>
