Venezuela between ELN delegates and the High Commissioner for
Peace, Victor G. Ricardo, and representatives from different non-
governmental sectors of the Colombian society.
</P>
<P>
The first meeting took place on February 9-11 between Ricardo
and Antonio Garcia, the second figure in the command of the ELN.
</P>
<P>
