<HEADLINE> Brazil to Hold UN Conference on Desertification </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, September 22 (Xinhua) -- Brazil is to hold the third
UN Desertification Conference on November 15-26.
</P>
<P>
According to the document signed between the Brazilian
government and the United Nations on Wednesday, the meeting will
be held in Recife, the capital of the northeastern state of
Pernambuc.
</P>
<P>
